FUNCTION getCanvasKit(options?) -> Promise<CanvasKit> [2026-03-26]       EXPORT
  Returns the cached instance immediately if already initialized. Otherwise calls CanvasKitInit with a locateFile resolver that prefixes "/" in browser environments or uses the bare filename in Node. Stores and returns the result.
